text: Savoia-Marchetti heavy fighter prototypes may refer to: * Savoia-Marchetti SM.88 * Savoia-Marchetti SM.91 * Savoia-Marchetti SM.92 All three were Italian twin-engined heavy fighter prototypes of World War II. All featured a dual- fuselage structure and used German Daimler-Benz engines. Category:Savoia- Marchetti aircraft
title: Savoia-Marchetti heavy fighter prototypes
